---
title: Creamy Chicken and Leeks with basmati rice
description: Looking for a meal you can put together in a flash that the whole family is sure to love? This creamy chicken and leek dish is as easy to prepare as it is delicious. Suitable both for posh palates and picky eaters!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF211008_R217_W47_FR_QFR20161847-1_MB_Main_high-1f8f859d.jpg
